*[[Aphakia]]<ref name="tsbvi">{{cite web |url=http://www.tsbvi.edu/Education/anomalies/Photophobia.htm |title=Photophobia |publisher=[[Texas School for the Blind and Visually Impaired]] |accessdate=December 11, 2009 }} {{Dead link|date=September 2010|bot=H3llBot}}</ref> (absence of the lens of the eye)
*[[Buphthalmos]]<ref name="taylor" /> (abnormally narrow angle between the cornea and iris)
*[[Cataracts]]<ref name="taylor" />
*[[Coloboma]]
*[[Cone dystrophy]]<ref name="taylor" />
*[[Congenital disorder|Congenital abnormalities]] of the eye<ref name="taylor" />
*[[Pinkeye|Viral conjunctivitis]] ("pink eye")<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.merck.com/mmpe/sec09/ch101/ch101c.html |title=Conjunctivitis |publisher=[[Merck Manual of Diagnosis and Therapy]] |accessdate=December 11, 2009 }}</ref>
