*[[Encephalitis]]<ref name="taylor" /> including Myalgic encephalomyelitis aka [[Chronic fatigue syndrome]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.healthsystem.virginia.edu/uvahealth/adult_infectious/cfs.cfm |title=Chronic Fatigue Syndrome |publisher=[[University of Virginia Health System]] |accessdate=December 11, 2009}}</ref>
